Package: MOGTree
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Objective Gain Trees for Personalized Treatment Decisions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yao", "Song", email = "yaos@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Chang", "Wang", role = "aut"),
    person("Lu", "Wang", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Fits multi-objective gain trees (MOG-Trees) that partition
    patients into subgroups with distinct treatment-outcome contrast profiles.
    The package includes tree construction, leaf prediction, propensity score
    estimation, regression-based outcome modeling, and augmented inverse
    probability weighted estimators that can be used to summarize treatment
    preferences across outcome weights.
